additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Glycerin, Aqua, Propylene Glycol, Aroma, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Benzoic Acid, Sodium Saccharin, Sodium Hydroxide.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Use as directed. This is not a contraceptive, doesn't contain spermicide and may slow sperm down. Avoid contact with eyes, broken skin or wounds. If you experience irritation stop use. Consult your doctor if irritation continues, you experience persistent vaginal dryness, are pregnant or breast-feeding. Keep out of reach of children. Keep out of the reach of children.
